OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fand very warm through the evening with
OL,7,Fsome late sunshine. Skies remaining
OL,8,Fclear overnight with light winds.
OL,9,FAnother very warm and muggy night to
OL,10,Fcome.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA dry, warm and sunny start.
OL,13,FTurning even hotter than Wednesday
OL,14,Fwith extreme heat continuing and high
OL,15,Fhumidity. Perhaps a little cloudier at
OL,16,Ftimes in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
